        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "For a single pile, one sees that an empty pile has value 0, a pile of 2 has value 1, a pile of 3 has value 2, a pile of 4 has value 0, a pile of 5 has value 1, and a pile of 6 has value 0.",
        "bbox": [
